This file, helpers.doc, is a note of thanks to all the people who
have helped in the development of Ghostscript.

For an overview of Ghostscript and a list of the documentation files, see
README.

Major contributors
------------------

Special thanks are due to Russell Lang, for the gsview (Ghostview for
Microsoft Windows) program and for contributing most of the code for
the Microsoft Windows environment, and to Tim Theisen, for the
Ghostview program for X Windows and for major contributions to the
code for the X Windows environment.

